gnu.expr
Class Symbol

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--gnu.expr.Symbol
public class Symbol
extends java.lang.Object

Utility class containing various routines to manipulate Scheme symbols. Note Scheme symbols are represented using java.lang.String objects, and there are no Symbol objects.
